@Helbound wrote:

what is the object ID of the portal you made. To see what the object ID is, go on your server using mopar’s client, and right click the portal you want to use. There should be a number next to the ‘examine’ option. If that number doesnt match the ‘Case’ number (4387) then change the ‘4387’ to the portals ID number. If you need more help, pm me.
